snippet.title: Looney Tunes World of Mayhem Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Get your anvils, boulders, pianos, and other ACME-branded instruments of destruction ready: Looney Tunes World of Mayhem from Scopely and Warner Bros. Interactive Entertainment is now officially available as a free download on the App Store and Google Play!
